      "SummaryText": "ludes information on emergency health care.\n\nPlanned Changes to Improve Safety\n\nGas Innovations understands that the facility has in place all required procedures to comply with applicable regulations to protect both the health and safety of its employees, the surrounding community and the environment.  Periodic safety and pollution prevention reviews are performed of processes, procedures and the facility in general, to assure the site complies with all applicable regulations in the prevention of accidental releases that can affect the safety and health of its employees, the surrounding community and the environment.\n\nRMP Submission\n\nThis RMP is being submitted on the June 28, 2023."
